info.title: SearchAPI - Google Search
info.description: Google Search service scrapes SERP for real-time results. Scrape organic results, ads, related searches, inline questions and more.

people_also_search_for_link.description: The people also search for link.
people_also_search_for_link.title: People Also Search For Link

get.description: Retrieve the Google Search result page (SERP) for a search query.

parameters.name: engine
parameters.description: The engine that will be used to retrieve real-time data.

parameters.name: q
parameters.description: The query you want to search. You can use anything that you would use in a regular Google search. e.g. inurl:, site:, intitle:, as_dt and as_eq.

parameters.name: device
parameters.description: The device that defines the search results.

parameters.name: location
parameters.description: The location where the search originated.

parameters.name: uule
parameters.description: The Google encoded location where the search originated.

parameters.name: google_domain
parameters.description: The Google domain of the search.

parameters.name: hl
parameters.description: The interface language of the search.

parameters.name: lr
parameters.description: Restricts search results to documents written in a particular language or a set of languages. The accepted format for this parameter is lang_{2-letter country code}.

parameters.name: cr
parameters.description: Restricts search results to documents originating in a particular country.

parameters.name: nfpr
parameters.description: Whether results from queries that have been auto-corrected for spelling errors are included. To exclude, set to 1.

parameters.name: filter
parameters.description: Whether the "Duplicate Content" and "Host Crowding" filters are enabled. Set the value to 1 to enable these filters.

parameters.name: safe
parameters.description: Whether SafeSearch is active or not.

parameters.name: num
parameters.description: The number of results to display per page.

parameters.name: page
parameters.description: The page of results to return.
